imdb.plot outline: Jeff Holiday and Nick Goroff (Wizard of Cause) host the online late night talk shows The Youtube Saints, interviewing fellow Youtube creators, as well as actors, comedians and writers. Beginning with a three to five piece news segment, the pair enjoy strong drink and offer relentless comedic banter about the stories of the week. Then, joined by a special guest each week, the show explores the oddities of online culture, current affairs or special interest, before moving on to throw a spotlight onto lesser known content creators their guest believes deserves the attention. Capping each episode with jokes and analysis of that week's "Viral Cringe," Youtube Saints serves up a conventional late night format with the sorts of twisted humor that only the internet can offer.
